	<h1 class="title">21 世纪的太空竞赛，社交网络也成了战场</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/244919/small/244919.jpg?1451146107" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">李硕明 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-23 21:58:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19546/medium/19546.jpg?1450787999" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


